Description: Estimates the Joint Sentiment Topic model and its reversed version, 
    as described by Lin and He, 2009 <DOI:10.1145/1645953.1646003> and Lin, He, Everson and Ruger 
    (2012) <DOI:10.1109/TKDE.2011.48>.
